<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Spec 015 (F-3) — base wizard strings.

  Base language: EN per spec 015 clarification C-6 + A-15b (overrides ADR-004
  RU-first default for this module). Rationale: F-3 ships 11 locales total;
  EN is the canonical source for AI-driven translation (procedure-translate-
  spec-strings skill) targeting AR/HI/ZH/JA/KK where Russian is not a
  reasonable source.

  Per-key context lives in core/strings-context/CONTEXT.json (FR-031b).
  Glossary of canonical terms lives in core/GLOSSARY.md (FR-031c).
-->
